(18, 1, '2016-12-30 13:20:04', '2016-12-30 13:20:04', 'Itâ€™s the music that makes your ears prick up, the art that turns your head, the ideas that fuel your mind, the thinkers, the makers, the movers the shakers. Whether youâ€™re looking for inspiration, words of wisdom from creative professionals or something interesting to read, feast your eyes on Amavi.\r\n\r\nGet your fix of art, music, design, fashion, photography, creative entrepreneurial projects and film.\r\n<p style="text-align: left;"><em>Veni, vidi, amavi.</em></p>\r\n<p style="text-align: left;"><em>I came, I saw, I loved.</em></p>\r\n<p style="text-align: left;"><b>Ruth Dunn</b>\r\nFounder &amp; Editor\r\nTo write.</p>', 'Who We Are', '', 'publish', 'closed', 'closed', '', 'about', '', '', '2018-03-15 13:03:50', '2018-03-15 13:03:50', '', 0, 'http://localhost:8888/?page_id=18', 0, 'page', '', 0),
