€˜Thereâ€™s an app for thatâ€™ age. So if you havenâ€™t already flirted with the idea of launching your own app, youâ€™ve almost certainly had a fleeting idea for one before (probably) tossing it into the â€˜too hardâ€™ basket.</section>', '5 things you should know before launching your own app', '', 'inherit', 'closed', 'closed', '', '23-revision-v1', '', '', '2017-01-15 21:14:32', '2017-01-15 21:14:32', '', 23, 'http://localhost:8888/2017/01/15/23-revision-v1/', 0, 'revision', '', 0),
